FOLDER.DESCRIPTION: CDW_Shared Folder should contain all source and target definitions, as well as all reusable transformations and mapplets.

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: To pick up the patron id thanks to the legacypatronid. EndEffDt is inclusive, so a range of 1/8/2004 to 10/8/2004 actually means 12:00am on 1/8 to 11:59pm on 10/8. In order to use datetime inputs, it is necessary to add 1 to the EndEffDt and use a less-than operator. eg. PromoDtTm < EndEffDt + 1 will match PromoDtTm up to 11:59:59 on the day of EndEffDt.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: Lkp_Patron

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT uvw_Lkp_Patron.PATRONID as PATRONID , uvw_Lkp_Patron.CROWNCLUBJOINDT as CROWNCLUBJOINDT , uvw_Lkp_Patron.DOB as DOB , uvw_Lkp_Patron.LEGACYPATRONID as LEGACYPATRONID , uvw_Lkp_Patron.BEGEFFDT as BEGEFFDT , uvw_Lkp_Patron.ENDEFFDT as ENDEFFDT ,uvw_Lkp_Patron.SiteId as SiteID FROM uvw_Lkp_Patron

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: LEGACYPATRONID = IN_LEGACYPATRONID AND SiteID = IN_SiteID AND BEGEFFDT <= IN_PROMOTIONTRANSACTIONDATE AND ENDEFFDT > IN_PROMOTIONTRANSACTIONDATE
